OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782910143
OL,3,CFly-tipper has car crushed as part of
OL,4,Ccouncil crackdown on illegal dumping
OL,6,FA fly-tipper who dumped plastic pipes
OL,7,Fon a footpath in Wiltshire has had his
OL,8,Fcar seized and crushed as part of a
OL,9,Fcrackdown on illegally discarding
OL,10,Fwaste in the county.
OL,12,FThe man was seen on CCTV leaving the
OL,13,Fpipes on a public right of way in
OL,14,FBulford last May.
OL,16,FHis vehicle was then seized as part of
OL,17,Fa joint investigation by Wiltshire
OL,18,FCouncil and Wiltshire Police.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
