PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782910143
OL,3,CFly-tipper has car crushed as part of
OL,4,Ccouncil crackdown on illegal dumping
OL,6,FHe was also fined #1,000 - which
OL,7,Fremains unpaid - and ordered to
OL,8,Fprovide proof of ownership of the
OL,9,Fvehicle within a 15-day period.
OL,11,FWhen this was not given, the vehicle
OL,12,Fwas legally forfeited to the council,
OL,13,Fwhich made the decision to scrap it.
OL,15,FThe authority then put the car on
OL,16,Fdisplay outside County Hall, in
OL,17,FTrowbridge, to highlight the
OL,18,Fconsequences of fly-tipping and act as
OL,19,Fa deterrent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
